        <h2>The Path of the Dark Mother</h2>
        <p>This is a private, serious occult order centered on Lilith in her ancient form as the Queen of the Night and creatrix of the night side.</p>
        <p>We work directly with her current through ritual, study of primary sources (Mesopotamian Lilitu lore, Zohar, Alphabet of Ben Sira), and personal practice. The focus is real experiential gnosis and birthing personal power from the Qliphothic realms.</p>
        
        <h2>Who This Order Is For</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Practitioners who approach Lilith with genuine respect and commitment</li>
            <li>Those willing to do the work: regular dark moon rituals, study, and honest self-confrontation</li>
            <li>Seekers who treat the occult as living reality, not entertainment or symbolism</li>
        </ul>
        
        <div class="warning">
            This path demands sincerity. Mockery, spectacle, or treating the work as a game will result in removal. 
            The current itself filters the unworthy.
        </div>
        
        <h2>How to Begin</h2>
        <p>If you are serious about joining:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Perform the solitary Burney Relief invocation during the next dark moon.</li>
            <li>Document any vision, sign, or personal result you receive.</li>
            <li>Contact the council with your experience for review.</li>
        </ol>
        <p>Entry is by invitation only after successful initiation.</p>
        
        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 50px; font-size: 0.9em;">
            Private • Serious • Initiatory<br>
            Lilith guards her own.
